%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hug, to embrace","examples":[{"text":"سَهِرْتُ لَيْلَ أَخِي ذُبْيَانَ أَحْضُنُهُ / حَضْنَ الرَّوَاضِعِ بَيْنَ الْعَتِّ وَٱللِّينِ"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to incubate, to hatch"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to nurse, to raise, to rear"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deter, to keep off"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"breast; bosom"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"spread arms; armful"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَضَنَ (ḥaḍana) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ivory"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a mountain in Najd"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hiding place of a hyena"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"foot of a mountain, base"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ح ض ن (ḥ ḍ n), from Proto-Semitic *ḥaṣ́an-. Compare Hebrew חֹצֶן (ḥṓṣen), Classical Syriac ܚܢܐ and Ge'ez ሐፀነ (ḥäṣ́änä)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8337","headword_ar":"حُضْنٌ","root":"HDn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8338","headword_ar":"حِضْنٌ","root":"HDn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part beneath the armpit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extending to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$oH","text_ar":"كَشْح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flank"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Msb, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bosom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sador","text_ar":"صَدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~adori","text_ar":"الصَّدْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~adoru","text_ar":"الصَّدْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper arms with what is between them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHotaDanN","text_ar":"مُحْتَضَنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (S:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoDaAnN","text_ar":"اَحْضَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K *) [and accord. to Freytag's Lex."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuDuwnN","text_ar":"حُضُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also]. ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing, (S, K,) and of a man: (Mgh:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lateral,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjacent, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoDaAnN","text_ar":"اَحْضَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, * K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiDonaA AlmafaAzapi","text_ar":"حِضْنَا المَفَازَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two borders"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the nearer border and the further"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the desert."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiDonaA All~ayoli","text_ar":"حِضْنَا اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first and last portions"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And [as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiDon","text_ar":"حِضْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man or woman is often a place of concealment,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA zaAla yaqoTaEu A^aHoDaAna All~ayoli","text_ar":"مَا زَالَ يَقْطَعُ اَحْضَانَ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ceased not to traverse the shades of the night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayokumo biAlHiDonayoni","text_ar":"عَلَيْكُمْ بِالحِضْنَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a trad. of 'Alee, means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keep ye to"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two wings of the army."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a fulaAnN Haq~ahu EalaY","text_ar":"اَخَذَ فُلَانٌ حَقَّهُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiDonihi","text_ar":"حِضْنِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one took his right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due, by force."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  Also (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity that is carried in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiDon","text_ar":"حِضْن"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) ―         -b4-  Also, (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuDonN","text_ar":"حُضْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"den,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subterranean habitation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the hyena: (S, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of hunting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of capture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the hyena. (IB, TA.) ―         -b5-  And, both these words, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circuit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surrounding part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a mountain: or its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"base;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest, part."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) Accord. to Az,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiDonaA Aljabali","text_ar":"حِضْنَا الجَبَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two lateral,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjacent, parts of the mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n8339","headword_ar":"حَضَنٌ","root":"HDn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ivory:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, K:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tush of the elephant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["ISk","S","K"]}]}}